  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to provide access to palbociclib in Mexico and in selected Latin
      American countries before it becomes commercially available to patients with HR
      positive/HER2-negative ABC who are appropriate candidates for letrozole therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
